  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Skeletons are invading, and your only defense is a toaster and a chicken! Embark on a whimsical adventure through a land plagued by pesky skeletons! Uncover weird and wacky weapon synergies to fight back against the bony baddies. Along the way, you'll gather a rag-tag group of heroes who will aid you on your mission- will you have the guts to stop the necromancer's plans and save the world?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1951650/extras/8f4f2c3a085c60d7bc72983e7092bd77.poster.avif?t=1754916772\" width=620 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1951650/extras/8f4f2c3a085c60d7bc72983e7092bd77.webm?t=1754916772\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Discover an arsenal of ONE MILLION different weapon combinations, from explosive toast to homing robot chickens, and customize your loadout to suit your playstyle as you wreak havoc on your enemies.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1951650/extras/8a6d84130cb6920218f547a3f61df4be.poster.avif?t=1754916772\" width=620 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1951650/extras/8a6d84130cb6920218f547a3f61df4be.webm?t=1754916772\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Recruit up to four friends to join your quest to defeat the necromancer, or measure yourself by playing alone.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1951650/extras/52a6d9091b71456ae9e4c9fb4df9ad35.poster.avif?t=1754916772\" width=620 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1951650/extras/52a6d9091b71456ae9e4c9fb4df9ad35.webm?t=1754916772\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Transform your train into a formidable base of operations for the friends you meet along the way, buy upgrades, decorate your train, and prepare your next mission!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1951650/extras/8d768345967c63f41ac1b1d822db00b2.poster.avif?t=1754916772\" width=620 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1951650/extras/8d768345967c63f41ac1b1d822db00b2.webm?t=1754916772\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>Dive into procedurally generated levels filled with challenges!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Test your skills and adaptability as you strive to overcome the ever-growing threats that await you.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Skeletons are invading, and your only defense is a toaster and a chicken! Embark on a whimsical adventure through a land plagued by pesky skeletons! Uncover weird and wacky weapon synergies to fight back against the bony baddies. Along the way, you'll gather a rag-tag group of heroes who will aid you on your mission- will you have the guts to stop the necromancer's plans and save the world?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1951650/extras/8f4f2c3a085c60d7bc72983e7092bd77.poster.avif?t=1754916772\" width=620 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1951650/extras/8f4f2c3a085c60d7bc72983e7092bd77.webm?t=1754916772\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Discover an arsenal of ONE MILLION different weapon combinations, from explosive toast to homing robot chickens, and customize your loadout to suit your playstyle as you wreak havoc on your enemies.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1951650/extras/8a6d84130cb6920218f547a3f61df4be.poster.avif?t=1754916772\" width=620 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1951650/extras/8a6d84130cb6920218f547a3f61df4be.webm?t=1754916772\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Recruit up to four friends to join your quest to defeat the necromancer, or measure yourself by playing alone.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p clas